---
import IndexLayout from '@/layouts/IndexLayout.astro'

const supportEmail = 'developer@totemgrid.dev'
---

<IndexLayout
  title="TotemGrid – Child Safety & CSAE Policy"
  description="TotemGrid prohibits child sexual abuse and exploitation (CSAE) and enforces strict safety standards."
>
  <main class="policy-page">
    <header class="hero card-depth" aria-labelledby="policy-heading">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <h1 id="policy-heading">TotemGrid – Child Safety &amp; CSAE Policy</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
          TotemGrid strictly prohibits any content, behavior, or activity related to child sexual abuse or exploitation (CSAE).
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="content card-depth" aria-label="Child safety and CSAE policy">
      <div class="content-inner">
        <p>
          TotemGrid currently operates as a status-based social coordination app. At present, the platform supports limited,
          text-based status updates and does not enable media sharing.
        </p>

        <p>
          The app is not intended for use by minors and does not allow sexual content involving children under any
          circumstances.
        </p>

        <p>
          If TotemGrid introduces additional communication features in the future, such features will be subject to the same CSAE
          prohibitions, moderation standards, and reporting obligations described in this policy.
        </p>

        <section aria-labelledby="actions-heading">
          <h2 id="actions-heading">If TotemGrid becomes aware of CSAE</h2>
          <p>We will:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Remove the content where technically feasible</li>
            <li>Suspend or terminate offending accounts</li>
            <li>
              Report the activity to appropriate authorities, including the National Center for Missing &amp; Exploited Children
              (NCMEC), where legally required
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <p>TotemGrid complies with all applicable child safety and online protection laws.</p>

        <p>
          Users who violate this policy will be removed from the platform without warning.
        </p>

        <section class="contact" aria-labelledby="contact-heading">
          <h2 id="contact-heading">Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Concerns or reports may be sent to:
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href={`mailto:${supportEmail}`}>{supportEmail}</a>
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</IndexLayout>

<style>
  .policy-page {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 56rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-inner h1 {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--colors-ink-98, #F2EFFF);
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  .content {
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--colors-ink-99, #FCF8FF);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .content-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 1rem 0 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--colors-ink-10);
  }

  p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  a {
    color: inherit;
  }

  .contact {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-top: 1rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
